Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.90,0:12:28.60,Main,Erina,0,0,0,,Mr. Smokey, I'd like you to join us. {I think it's appropriate Erina calls him "Smokey-san" or "Mr. Smokey" since it shows she sees him as an equal and not a minority, a very nice trait.}
